metadata.name: Btc Ordinal people 1/10000
metadata.description:
Bitcoin is the first application of blockchain technology, and with the increasing popularity of NFTs worldwide, Bitcoin-based NFTs are expected to become one of the future hotspots.
 However, ordinary people may find it difficult to participate, which is why we aim to collect 10,000 funding units as a source of funding to participate in the bidding for TwelveFold. 
Your donation will be directly used to pay for bidding fees and develop the necessary technical equipment and personnel. We expect to raise a total of 0.5 BTC by the end of the campaign, with the team reserving 300 tokens for future marketing and collaboration efforts, and relying on royalty income to support expenses.

Phase one: Establish a DAO to monitor the auction and maximize the use of funds to acquire the project.

Phase two: Discord members will use tokens to vote on the website and decide on the next BTC purchase project and the application of TwelveFold.
